		<title>17Recreation Grounds:Ferryhill</title>
		<content> There are recreation grounds in Ferry-
 hill at both Dean Bank and the Broom. 
 Both are maintained by Ferryhill Town 
 Council and provide facilities for    
 sport and outdoor activities.         
{Our Rec.                              
  Our rec. has football,tennis and a   
 bowling green.There is a pavilion to  
 change in.There is a playground with  
 a fort,swings,a slide and a climbing  
 frame.                                
  Our school football team plays down  
 the rec. and we have our school sports
 there.                                
       Dawn Metcalfe(age 9)            
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
